title: Product/Study : Canadian International Merchandise Trade Database, August 2015 (Statistics Canada)
text: ( Source : Statistics Canada ) The Canadian International Merchandise Trade ( CIMT ) online database offers detailed export and import trade data using the Harmonized System (HS) classification of goods (based on the 6-digit commodity level).
